text: Bismillah Zadran (born 4 January 1990) is an Afghan cricketer. He made his List A debut for Khost Province in the 2019 Afghanistan Provincial Challenge Cup tournament on 31 July 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Afghan cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
